    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change GCSEs and A Levels so there is a greater emphasis on coursework\r\n",
        "additional_details": "We think that current exams only prove that students can memorise information temporarily and that they may quickly forget what they have learnt.",
        "background": "Change these courses to make them more coursework based so students are not so reliant on exams, which may not always give the best results. We think this will be fairer for everyone and you will see more understanding of the topic and information that students need to know.",
